msgctxt "an5.216:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.216:0.2"
msgid "22. Akkosakavagga "
msgstr "22. Abuse "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.216:0.3"
msgid "216. Dutiyaakkhantisutta "
msgstr "216. Intolerance (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.255, sc1
msgctxt "an5.216:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā akkhantiyā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks of intolerance. "

msgctxt "an5.216:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.216:1.3"
msgid "Bahuno janassa appiyo hoti amanāpo, luddo ca hoti, vippaṭisārī ca, sammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Most people find you unlikable and unlovable. You’re cruel and remorseful. You feel lost when you die. And when your body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "an5.216:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ādīnavā akkhantiyā. "
msgstr "These are the five drawbacks to intolerance. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.216:2.1"
msgid "Pañcime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā khantiyā. "
msgstr "There are these five benefits of tolerance. "

msgctxt "an5.216:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.216:2.3"
msgid "Bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo, aluddo ca hoti, avippaṭisārī ca, asammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Most people find you likable and lovable. You’re neither cruel nor remorseful. You don’t feel lost when you die. And when your body breaks up, after death, you’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "

msgctxt "an5.216:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca ānisaṃsā khantiyā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five benefits of tolerance.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.216:2.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

